WRZZ is a Classic rock formatted broadcast radio station licensed to Parkersburg, West Virginia, United States, serving the Parkersburg/Marietta area.  WRZZ is owned and operated by 
Seven Mountains Media. The station is an affiliate of the syndicated Pink Floyd program "Floydian Slip".
On June 26, 2024, WRZZ rebranded as "106.1 The Goat".


